    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Before you pack your camping gear for your next outdoor adventure, be sure to grab a handful of the ASR Outdoor Glow in the Dark Universal Heavy Duty Twisted Metal PVC Camping Gear Canopy Tent Stakes. Easy to install, durable, versatile and easy to spot at night or in low light conditions due to the glow in the dark topper, these heavy-duty tent pegs will soon become a staple in your backpacking, trekking and camping gear! The tent stakes feature sharp square-pointed tips, a twisted metal body design, large heavy-duty PVC toppers and a stringing eyelet on top of the plastic topper for anchoring versatility</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Universal Camping Steel Tent Stakes Heavy Duty Replacement Pegs</h2>\n  <p>Before you pack your camping gear for your next outdoor adventure, be sure to grab a handful of the ASR Outdoor Glow in the Dark Universal Heavy Duty Twisted Metal PVC Camping Gear Canopy Tent Stakes. Easy to install, durable, versatile and easy to spot at night or in low light conditions due to the glow in the dark topper, these heavy-duty tent pegs will soon become a staple in your backpacking, trekking and camping gear!</p>\n  <p>The tent stakes feature sharp square-pointed tips, a twisted metal body design, large heavy-duty PVC toppers and a stringing eyelet on top of the plastic topper for anchoring versatility. The tent stakes feature a deliberate twisted metal body design that easily penetrates everything from hard packed soil to grass and sand; the tent pegs will hold strong against bad weather or heavy winds wherever you need to secure a canopy, tent, pergola or overhead covering.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>CAMPING GEAR ESSENTIAL:</strong> The ASR Outdoor camping tent stakes are an essential item to pack with your camping gear; the tent stakes feature sharp square-pointed tips, twisted metal body design, large heavy-duty PVC stoppers and a stringing eyelet on top of the plastic stopper for anchoring versatility and easy installation</li>\n    <li><strong>GLOW IN THE DARK TOPPERS:</strong> The tent stakes glow brightly in the dark, helping to locate tent pegs at night or in low light conditions; the glow in the dark feature also allows you to easily maintain, fix or adjust the tent stakes without needed a flashlight or headlamp</li>\n    <li><strong>TWISTED METAL DESIGN:</strong> The tent stakes feature a deliberate twisted metal body design that easily penetrates everything from hard packed soil to sand; the tent pegs will hold strong against bad weather or heavy winds wherever you need to secure an overhead covering, canopy, tent, pergola and more</li>\n    <li><strong>DURABLE GALVANIZED STEEL:</strong> The tent stakes to tent pegs are constructed from galvanized steel, meaning a protective zinc coating is placed over top of the steel in order to prevent any rusting or corrosion; the tent pegs material is incredibly durable and sturdy, sure to last through many camping seasons and backpacking adventures</li>\n    <li><strong>MULTIPURPOSE TENT STAKE:</strong> Whether you are installing a tent, grow tent, canopy, camping tent, beach tent, pop up tent, tarp tent, pergola or overhead covering for a wedding, picnic, sporting event or other, the tent stakes can handle all of it and with the handy stringing eyelet on top of the plastic stopper, installation will be a breeze</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/tent_stake_parent_all.jpg\" alt=\"Before you pack your camping gear for your next outdoor adventure, be sure to grab a handful of the ASR Outdoor Glow in the Dark Universal Heavy Duty\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 73601</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 746448557088</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>In addition to the functional twisted metal design feature, the tent pegs are constructed from durable and long-lasting galvanized steel, meaning a protective zinc coating is placed over top of the steel in order to prevent rusting or corrosion. The tent peg material is incredibly sturdy and rust-resistant, sure to last you through many camping seasons and backpacking adventures to come. Plus, the large topper makes hammering easy and, because the PVC toppers glow in the dark easily maintain, fix or adjust the tent stakes without a flashlight or headlamp.</p>\n  <p>Whether installing a tent, grow tent, canopy, camping tent, beach tent, pop up tent, tarp tent, pergola or overhead covering for a wedding, picnic, sporting event or other, the tent stakes can handle all of the aforementioned, and with the handy stringing eyelet on top of the plastic topper, installation will be a breeze.</p>\n  <p>Available Pack Sizes: 4, 8, 10 or 20 Stakes</p>\n  <p>SPECIFICATIONS: Length: 10.5 inches; Thickness: 7mm; Material: Galvanized High Carbon Steel</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
